This framework pairs with, but does not bundle, a separate set of review agents
published at https://github.com/eranw2000/claude-review-agents (code-reviewer,
deploy-guard, pr-validator). Those agents are installed separately; the
pr-checkpoint skill uses them if present and skips them if not.
